Sam Peterson was an additional helper. Sunny

Weather was rainy and cloudy. Lake seemed high due to recent rainfall. 2 loons (possibly juvenile common loons) were on the lake. Water towards the boat landing was very murky and brown. Towards the middle of the lake was clear.
Cloudy- cool- and breezy. Mikaela Zenz was additional helper.
Colton Hahn and Mikaela Zenz took measurements. Very windy- partly sunny- moderate temp of 65F.

Mikaela Zenz and Matt Pfaff took measurements. Sunny- warm- windy and somewhat humid. Moderate temp of 74F.
